name: Correlation plots of double knockout distribution across subsystems in M.tb and E.coli

desc.html: Plot of correlation matrix with clustering of double knockout distributions across sub-systems in E.coli and M.tuberculosis.

wiki.Credit: I used the BFD_Processor function in my R package abcdeFBA to assemble files containing double knockout data generated by the Exhaustive_double_deletion function in abcdeFBA.
